{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"913aee6c88","title":"给陈嘉庚“的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"050e71e420","index":0,"year":1949,"month":1,"day":20,"articleId":"913aee6c88"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji26","name":"毛泽东全集第26卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji26.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji26":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"a4d9392662","type":"paragraph","text":"给陈嘉庚“的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji26","articleId":"913aee6c88"},{"id":"ab6e4520d8","type":"paragraph","text":"（1949年1月20日）嘉庆先生：中国人民解放斗争日益接近全国胜利，需召开新的政治协商会议，建立民主联合政府，团结全国人民及海外侨胞力量，完成中国人民独立解放事业。为此录待各民主党派及各界领袖共同商讨。先生南侨硕望，人望所归，谨请命驾北来，参加会议。肃电欢迎，并祈赐复。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji26","articleId":"913aee6c88"},{"id":"160756e327","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji26","articleId":"913aee6c88"},{"id":"e4b880a64d","type":"paragraph","text":"一九四九年一月二十日[I]陈嘉皮（1874-1961），建厦门人，爱国华侨领袖。1949年应邀回国参加中国人民政治协商会议第一届全停会议。建国后，曾任中央人民政府委员、政协全国委员会副主席、全国人大常委会委员、中华全国归图华","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji26","articleId":"913aee6c88"}],"page":{"id":"d2914c67b8","publicationId":"maoquanji26","articleId":"913aee6c88","start":39,"end":39}}}},"__N_SSG":true}